data.description: Experience the epitome of comfort with this meticulously maintained Clovis residence, boasting four expansive bedrooms, a versatile loft, and three full bathrooms. Crafted in 2020 by Wathen Castanos, this home is a masterpiece of contemporary design offering the luxury of a newly constructed home with thoughtful upgrades. Located in the highly desirable Clovis Unified School District and a short walk from the community park and walking trails, this home is everything you're looking for and more. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the warm and welcoming atmosphere of this beautiful home. You'll love the thoughtful details and upgrades including; custom window coverings, living room surround sound, security system and impeccable low maintenance landscaping complete with synthetic lawn. You will adore the perfectly appointed open floor plan with a spacious kitchen which features granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances. The spacious primary suite is a true oasis, featuring a walk-in closet, dual sink vanity and luxurious spa tub. This masterfully designed home is located in a sought-after, family-friendly community that's just a short walk from local parks, schools, eateries, and coffee shops. It's the ideal home for anyone seeking a convenient and comfortable lifestyle in a welcoming neighborhood.
